file access issues.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugins can be sorted as well.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>A few improvements related to WordPress 4.6.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>A few improvements related to WordPress 4.5.0.<br \/>\nInitial Release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-1.gif?rev=2317044\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-1.gif?rev=2317044\" alt=\"How it works?\"><\/a><p>How it works?<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1361262\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1361262\" alt=\"Settings Page\"><\/a><p>Settings Page<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2317044\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2317044\" alt=\"Installation &amp; Activation\"><\/a><p>Installation &amp; Activation<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2317044\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-sort-order\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2317044\" alt=\"Settings Page - Full\"><\/a><p>Settings Page - Full<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best all in one Sort Plugin with usefull setting and intuitive interface<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/spencerjakobgm\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2dc4777d10a35346321efb3ff352ddeb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2dc4777d10a35346321efb3ff352ddeb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/spencerjakobgm\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">spencerjakobgm<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 21, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Best all in one Sort Plugin with usefull setting and intuitive interface and capabilities\/ permission settings<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">So editors, which are allowed to create new terms\/ categories are also allowed to sort the terms. Not common at other sort term plugins with much higher installation base.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Thank you Fahad for this great plugin.<br \/>Spencer<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Really good plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/aleph2u\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/92c0f344ff6b24193d31a6b82be04349?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/92c0f344ff6b24193d31a6b82be04349?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/aleph2u\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aleph2u<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 12, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best plugin to order pages, posts and custom post types!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very convenient sorting tool<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"s